        <h2>What is llms.txt?</h2>
        <p>llms.txt is an emerging standard that lets websites control how AI crawlers access their content. Enter your website URL above to auto-crawl your site, detect content types, and generate a validated llms.txt file with proper AI crawler controls.</p>
