        <li><strong>Documentation Sites</strong> — Allow API docs and guides for AI training. Set clear attribution requirements for technical content.</li>
        <li><strong>News & Media</strong> — Require attribution for all AI use of reporting. Block subscription-only content while allowing public articles.</li>
